description: This file defines the ProductService interface, specifying the business operations for managing products such as create, findAll, findById, update, and delete.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Creates a new product with provided request data

methods.name: findAll
methods.description: Retrieves a list of all products

methods.name: findById
methods.description: Finds a product by its unique identifier

methods.name: update
methods.description: Updates an existing product identified by id with new data

methods.name: delete
methods.description: Deletes the product with the specified id
